bug.short_desc: Number and Date formating in Table tests (Table_1.html etc.) broken

long_desc.thetext:
The number columns display the text "cldr_number_decimal_separator" instead of a dot or a comma.
The date columns diplay additional questionmarks and the text cldr_am instead of ":" or am/pm.
This worked in rev. 6770 in the 0.7 online tests at demo.qooxdoo.org.
It is broken in trunk rev. 6793.

Somehow building the localization did not work.
